<concept_spec>

concept SimulationType

purpose
    to manage different types of simulations available in the platform, their configurations, and metadata

state
    a set of Types with
        an id String
        a name String
        a description String
        a category String
        a icon String
        a thumbnail String
        a isActive Boolean
        a defaultConfig Object
        a requirements Object
        a version String

actions
    register (id: String, name: String, description: String, category: String, icon: String, thumbnail: String, defaultConfig: Object, requirements: Object, version: String) : (id: String)
        register a new simulation type
        return the type id
    update (id: String, name: String, description: String, category: String, icon: String, thumbnail: String, defaultConfig: Object, requirements: Object, version: String) : (id: String)
        update simulation type metadata
        return the type id
    activate (id: String) : (id: String)
        activate a simulation type
        return the type id
    deactivate (id: String) : (id: String)
        deactivate a simulation type
        return the type id
    updateDefaultConfig (id: String, defaultConfig: Object) : (id: String)
        update the default configuration for a simulation type
        return the type id

queries
    _getById (id: String) : (id: String, name: String, description: String, category: String, icon: String, thumbnail: String, isActive: Boolean, defaultConfig: Object, requirements: Object, version: String)
        get simulation type by id
    _getActive () : (id: String, name: String, description: String, category: String, icon: String, thumbnail: String, isActive: Boolean, defaultConfig: Object, requirements: Object, version: String)
        get all active simulation types
    _getByCategory (category: String) : (id: String, name: String, description: String, category: String, icon: String, thumbnail: String, isActive: Boolean, defaultConfig: Object, requirements: Object, version: String)
        get all simulation types in a category
    _getFeatured () : (id: String, name: String, description: String, category: String, icon: String, thumbnail: String, isActive: Boolean, defaultConfig: Object, requirements: Object, version: String)
        get featured simulation types

operational principle
    after register (id: "solar-system", name: "Solar System", description: "Interactive solar system simulation", category: "astronomy", icon: "ðŸŒž", thumbnail: "solar-system.jpg", defaultConfig: {speed: 1.0}, requirements: {threejs: true}, version: "1.0") : (id: "solar-system")
    and activate (id: "solar-system") : (id: "solar-system")
    then _getActive () shows the solar system simulation type as available for project creation

</concept_spec>
